## Git Strategy Matrix (SSOT)

Use skill-specific git behavior from a single source of truth:

- `plan`: strict preflight + branch preparation (`harness git-preflight`, `harness git-prepare-branch`)
- `build`: low-interference mode; avoid implicit branch rewrites
- `eval`: read-only diagnostics only; no implicit branch mutation
- `ship`: full automation with sync/rebase/error-code handling
- `investigate`: isolated branch debugging flow
- `doc-release`: follow current task branch; no new long-lived branch

All role prompts should reference this matrix and avoid ad-hoc raw git snippets when a structured command exists.
